	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;546&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1310px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;首次购买的服务器需要重置密码
&lt;img src=&#34;https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;596&#34;
	height=&#34;60&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-1_hu_4816c2c5dca4b21a.png 480w, https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-1_hu_490f0381cbb91c19.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;993&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;2384px&#34;
	
&gt;
可以使用阿里云自带的远程连接进行SSH工作。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我在这个服务器中安装了一个宝塔面板。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;安装教程&#34;&gt;安装教程
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.bt.cn/new/download.html&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;宝塔面板&lt;/a&gt;
进入服务器后台终端，输入命令。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1913&#34;
	height=&#34;953&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-2_hu_dcd5603ca3756ed0.png 480w, https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-2_hu_df18d05f97dedca.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;200&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;481px&#34;
	
&gt;
复制里面的代码&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;wget -O install_panel.sh &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://download.bt.cn/install/install_panel.sh&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://download.bt.cn/install/install_panel.sh&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp;&amp;amp; sudo bash install_panel.sh ed8484bec&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进行安装。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://xqwperfect.github.io/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/image-3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1845&#34;
